{
  "texts": [
    "The library offers parameter sets for different configurations depending on the application.",
    "Zama's Concrete [Zam22a] is a compiler for CGGI built on top of THFE-rs.",
    "It contains an optimizing tool foot_12 to find appropriate parameters for a given FHE computation.",
    "It makes use of the Lattice Estimator to find the security level of the parameters.",
    "Besides EVA, there have been other efforts proposing automatic scale management schemes for CKKS through compilers."
  ]
}